'''''The Galactic Encyclopedia''''' was an encyclopedia that documented nearly every major fact in the known universe. The book included an entry on [[Lightsaber/Legends|lightsabers]], which mentioned that [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] could make [[Synthetic lightsaber crystal/Legends|synthetic lightsaber crystals]] using a few basic elements and the power of [[The Force/Legends|the Force]].

Research for the project started shortly after the [[Ruusan campaign]], though it was curtailed with the formation of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]].

